      "message": "Can we change the order of these two test cases? Otherwise, you may have intermittently different notification created by cps-data-operations tests.\n\nIn which, stub url is given as dmi name. (${dmipluginCsitStubUrl}                 http://${DMI_CSIT_STUB_HOST}:${DMI_CSIT_STUB_PORT})\n\nHowever, dmi stub plugin may not have an healt check end point which make registered cm hanlde to send notification as you may seen on your local.",
